                                        "customFormula":  ""
                                    },
                        "description":  "For up to 10 minutes with concentration, the caster can use a Magic action each turn to affect one Huge or smaller creature or object within 60 feet: failed Strength saves let the caster move and Restrain creatures until the end of the caster\u0027s next turn, unattended objects move automatically, worn or carried objects can be pulled free on a failed save, and simple objects can be finely manipulated.",
